    "description": "Medix Inc. provides digital marketing services in Japan. It offers advertising and promotion services, such as search advertising, display advertising, feed ads, social media advertising, video ads, affiliate advertising, and advertising management service for agencies; creative design and production services, including creative consulting, EC site construction/ renewal, web advertising production, site construction and operation management, search engine optimization, and content marketing, as well as digital marketing services comprise web services, apps, DTP, videos, and novelties. The company also provides support to BtoC digital marketing and BtoB digital marketing support; and data-driven marketing services, such as data-driven marketing, data analysis support, CRM utilization support, GA4 usage support, and KARTE utilization support, KPI dashboard construction and organizational marketing support, and support for using BigQuery and BI tools. In addition, it offers tag management tools, overseas advertising distribution and overseas marketing support, in-house support service, and online advertising management services. Medix Inc. was incorporated in 1984 and is based in Tokyo, Japan."
